diagram:
graph TD;
A(Start: Hung task warnings appear) --> B(Identify D-state processes with ps); A --> C(Check /proc/<PID>/status and /proc/<PID>/fd);
B --> D(Attach strace and lsof to PID);
C --> D;
D --> E{Is the stall I/O-bound?}; E --> F[Yes: inspect disk/network I/O; No: inspect kernel timers/locks];
F --> G(Attempt graceful termination with SIGTERM);
G --> H{Terminated?}; H -- Yes --> I(Complete); H -- No --> J(Force kill after safety checks);
